{"tha-ap483:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap483:0.2":"Pamsukulavagga ","tha-ap483:0.3":"Pamsukulasannakattheraapadana ","tha-ap483:1.1":"“Tisso namasi bhagava, ","tha-ap483:1.2":"sayambhu aggapuggalo; ","tha-ap483:1.3":"Pamsukulam thapetvana, ","tha-ap483:1.4":"viharam pavisi jino. ","tha-ap483:2.1":"Vinatam dhanumadaya, ","tha-ap483:2.2":"bhakkhatthaya carim aham; ","tha-ap483:2.3":"Mandalaggam gahetvana, ","tha-ap483:2.4":"kananam pavisim aham. ","tha-ap483:3.1":"Tatthaddasam pamsukulam, ","tha-ap483:3.2":"dumagge laggitam tada; ","tha-ap483:3.3":"Capam tattheva nikkhippa, ","tha-ap483:3.4":"sire katvana anjalim. ","tha-ap483:4.1":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap483:4.2":"vipulaya ca pitiya; ","tha-ap483:4.3":"Buddhasettham saritvana, ","tha-ap483:4.4":"pamsukulam avandaham. ","tha-ap483:5.1":"Dvenavute ito kappe, ","tha-ap483:5.2":"pamsukulamavandaham; ","tha-ap483:5.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap483:5.4":"vandanaya idam phalam. ","tha-ap483:6.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap483:6.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap483:6.3":"Nagova bandhanam chetva, ","tha-ap483:6.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap483:7.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap483:7.2":"mama buddhassa santike; ","tha-ap483:7.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","tha-ap483:7.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap483:8.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap483:8.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap483:8.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap483:8.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap483:9.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma pamsukulasannako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap483:10.1":"Pamsukulasannakattherassapadanam pathamam. "}